data.title: Assembled Ceramic Table Lamp Blue - Threshold™
meta_keywords: Assembled Ceramic Table Lamp Blue - Threshold™
data.meta_description: Shop Assembled Ceramic Table Lamp Blue - Threshold™ at Target. Choose from Same Day Delivery, Drive Up or Order Pickup. Free standard shipping with $35 orders.
data.text:
Style up your contemporary decor with this Blue/White Medium Assembled Ceramic Table Lamp from Threshold™. This decorative table lamp makes a welcome addition to your indoor lighting. It features a blue and white abstract pattern on a bud-shaped ceramic base for modern flair. The off - white drum diffuses light with a warm, cozy glow, while the one-way light setting with an on/off switch allows for easy operation. Place it on the side table next to your sofa in your living room, on your console or sideboard to add some color and pattern to plain walls.

Threshold™: Looks like home, feels like you.
